    "body": "The module is only displayed by default if a remote SSH session is detected. The SSH connection is detected by checking environment variables `SSH_CONNECTION`, `SSH_CLIENT`, and `SSH_TTY`. Please ensure that these variables are preserved (e.g. via the sudo config) or set `hostname.ssh_only` to false (`starship config hostname.ssh_only false`). \n\nSince this has been reported before, I am closing this in favour of #6675 to keep discussion in one place.",
